Package: spacehakr
Title: Spatial Analysis, Raster Processing, and Geospatial Data Access
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Allan", "Irvine", , "al@newgraphenvironment.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3495-2128"))
Description: Tools for spatial analysis, raster processing, and geospatial data 
    access. Includes functions for GDAL/OpenDroneMap command building, GeoServer 
    WFS downloads, STAC catalog queries, spatial joins, and raster operations.
    Extracted from the ngr package's ngr_spk_* function family.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
